The following must be installed in order to fun the card application:
Visual C++ 9.0 (ak.ms/vcpython27)

These must be installed via pip.

(pip install {package})

Flask
flask_wtf
sqlalchemy
flask_sqlalchemy
passlib
Crypto

This must be installed via easy_install

(easy_install {package})

pycrypto

Please also ensure that 7z.exe is available in the system PATH

To run:
(With Command Prompt in same folder)
python cards.py

and the application will be available on localhost:5000